A student management system using PHP is a web-based application designed to efficiently manage various aspects of student information within an educational institution.

Steps to implement:
1. Download the zip folder from code section
2. unzip the file 
3. Download and install the Xampp control panel from any browser
4. Now place the whole folder to C:\xampp\htdocs
5. Open the Xampp application and Start the Apache and Mysql Services 
6. It is now serving in our local server open broswer and type localhost/index.php
